    {
      "id": "legend_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 660,
      "width": 1060,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "Legend\n\n🟦 Blue boxes = Player/UI layer (client-side)\n🟪 Purple boxes = Dialogue Manager (orchestration & parsing)\n🟧 Orange box = LocalAI LLM backend (:8080)\n🟩 Green boxes = RAG retrieval + Game State changes\n\nKey Design Decisions:\n1. Dialogue Manager is the single orchestration point — it sends to LLM, queries RAG, parses responses\n2. RAG retrieval happens BEFORE sending to LLM (context-enriched prompt)\n3. Action tags ([give_item:id=xxx]) are parsed server-side by SessionService after response completion\n4. Item trading uses ItemTradeService (NetworkBehaviour) for server-authoritative execution\n5. All state changes persist to Supabase via DialogueHistoryService",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#94a3b8",
      "originalText": "Legend\n\n🟦 Blue boxes = Player/UI layer (client-side)\n🟪 Purple boxes = Dialogue Manager (orchestration & parsing)\n🟧 Orange box = LocalAI LLM backend (:8080)\n🟩 Green boxes = RAG retrieval + Game State changes\n\nKey Design Decisions:\n1. Dialogue Manager is the single orchestration point — it sends to LLM, queries RAG, parses responses\n2. RAG retrieval happens BEFORE sending to LLM (context-enriched prompt)\n3. Action tags ([give_item:id=xxx]) are parsed server-side by SessionService after response completion\n4. Item trading uses ItemTradeService (NetworkBehaviour) for server-authoritative execution\n5. All state changes persist to Supabase via DialogueHistoryService",
      "autoResize": true
    }
